title: #92Noon! Montage/CC/Larrivee/Gleeman/JG
description: Montage gets you ready for the "Boom," and then Courtney Cronin is in studio for an hour. Border Battle check-in with Packers vox Wayne Larrivee, then Gleeman is in for most of the final hour. Justin Gaard wraps #92Noon with weekly Gopher football opinions!
